@NODE About "About"

Welcome to the fortunates.library v1.4! This Amiga-library contains
lots of handy and smart routines. Not only for the pure speed of
the assembler language but to offer a more efficient way of coding.

It's mainly for the coders in Assembler, Blitz Basic 2 and maybe
Amiga-E too (Check out if there are emodules in this archive).


  Check the Fortunates Wolf Page for the most current revision:

       -->  http://utopia.knoware.nl/users/sonicwlf/  <--
@ENDNODE

@NODE Installation "Installation"

Just put the file 'fortunates.library' in your LIBS: directory.
@ENDNODE

